<b>Pangea.org</b> or <b>Pangea</b> is a non-profit supporting organisation, which has been working for <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../948/329948.xml">
social change</link> since <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../598/34598.xml">
1993</link>. It "facilitates communication" through the use of information and communication technologies as e-mail, web content, free software and any other Internet service. Although it works with the <body wordnetid="107965085" confidence="0.8">
<social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
<group wordnetid="100031264" confidence="0.8">
<administration wordnetid="108164585" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../036/514036.xml">
Association for Progressive Communications</link></administration>
</group>
</social_group>
</body>
 in international projects its activity is focused on <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../239/9239.xml">
Europe</link> / <system wordnetid="108435388" confidence="0.8">
<economy wordnetid="108366753" confidence="0.8">
